OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNupur Sharma: India court  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsays Prophet row 'set      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcountry on fire'           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, India's top court has rebuked a former 
OL,6, spokesperson of the ruling party for   
OL,7, her controversial remarks on the       
OL,8, Prophet Muhammad.                      
OL,10,FThe court told Nupur Sharma that "her  
OL,11,Floose tongue has set the entire country
OL,12,Fon fire".                              
OL,14,FHer remarks in a TV debate sparked     
OL,15,Fviolence in some parts of the country  
OL,16,Fand also led to several Islamic nations
OL,17,Fregistering strong protests with India.
OL,19,FThe court also asked her to appear on a
OL,20,FTV channel and apologise to the nation.
